#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_mp3_e2.md:1
msgid "Hercules DJControl MP3 e2 / MP3 LE / Glow"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_mp3_e2.md:4
msgid "The Hercules DJ Control MP3 e2, MP3 LE, and Glow are USB controllers that have identical controls and share the same mapping. These controllers do not have a built in sound card, so a {ref}`splitter cable <hardware-splitter-cables>` or {ref}`separate audio interface <hardware-audio-interfaces>` is recommended for use with it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_mp3_e2.md:11
msgid "This new version is intended to work in a more intuitive way. Once you click on a button, it does its original function."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_mp3_e2.md:14
msgid "These controllers are not class compliant {term}`MIDI` devices. On Linux, older versions of Mixxx required using a custom Hercules kernel module. This is neither necessary not recommended anymore."
msgstr ""

